# VITA WISE AI - Food Log Summary API Testing
# ทดสอบ API endpoints สำหรับ food log summary

### 1. Login เพื่อดึง JWT Token
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. ทดสอบ Food Log Summary - Day Period with Custom Dates
# {{base_url}}/food-log/summary?period=day&startDate=2025-09-02&endDate=2025-09-02
GET http://localhost:3000/food-log/summary?period=day&startDate=2025-09-02&endDate=2025-09-02
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. ทดสอบ Food Log Summary - Week Period (Default)
# {{base_url}}/food-log/summary?period=week
GET http://localhost:3000/food-log/summary?period=week
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. ทดสอบ Food Log Summary - Month Period
# {{base_url}}/food-log/summary?period=month
GET http://localhost:3000/food-log/summary?period=month
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. ทดสอบ Food Log Summary - Day Period (Current Day)
GET http://localhost:3000/food-log/summary?period=day
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. ทดสอบ Food Log Summary - Custom Date Range
GET http://localhost:3000/food-log/summary?startDate=2025-09-01&endDate=2025-09-07
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. ทดสอบ Food Log Summary - No Parameters (Default Week)
GET http://localhost:3000/food-log/summary
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

